# Media Capture — Pathwaize Intelligence Center

## Hero flow captured

**Date:** Jul 1, 2026 | **Demo URL:** https://michaelwegter.com/demos/real-estate-intelligence-center/

**Captured flow:**
1. Page load (React SPA + AI workflow execution console visible)
2. Fill content brief input textarea ("Create a LinkedIn post on AI-driven real estate operations...")
3. Click "Run Authority Engine" button
4. Wait for mock LLM output (~2.5s)
5. Output card appears with "Needs Review" status + Approve/Request Edits/Push buttons
6. Click "Approve" button (Push button was disabled pre-approval, enabled post-approval)
7. Final state captured: approved output card with enabled Push button

